# Data Analytics Standards

## School Data Processing
- Follow data structure defined in [sgschooling_data_structure.md](mdc:sgschooling_data_structure.md)
- Use [extract_sgschooling_data.py](mdc:extract_sgschooling_data.py) as reference for data extraction patterns
- Handle CSV files like [ang_mo_kio_school_data.csv](mdc:ang_mo_kio_school_data.csv) with proper encoding

## Data Quality
- Implement data validation for all school data inputs
- Handle missing or malformed data gracefully
- Add logging for data processing operations
- Verify data integrity before database operations

## API Data Integration
- Reference [data_gov_sg_api_info.md](mdc:data_gov_sg_api_info.md) for external API guidelines
- Implement proper error handling for API calls
- Cache API responses appropriately to avoid rate limiting
- Handle API authentication and token management securely

## Performance Considerations
- Optimize database queries for school data retrieval
- Implement pagination for large datasets
- Use appropriate indexing for school search operations
- Cache frequently accessed school information

## Data Documentation
- Document all data transformations and calculations
- Keep [sgschooling_data_structure.md](mdc:sgschooling_data_structure.md) updated with schema changes
- Add comments for complex data processing logic
- Update [singapore_primary_school_overview.md](mdc:singapore_primary_school_overview.md) when adding new data sources
